  <brief_title>Intra Cranial EEG Activity During Dexmedetomidine Sedation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intra Cranial EEG Activity During Dexmedetomidine Sedation.Comparing the Effects of Dexmedetomidine on the Cortical and the Sub Cortical(Hippocampus) Structures.</official_title>
